[SN]TITLE[SN]
Murder arrest after body found in Llanrumney house fire

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
A woman has been arrested on suspicion of murder after the body of a man was found following a house fire in Cardiff.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
Police were called to Llanrumney Avenue, Llanrumney, at 04:30 GMT on Sunday.
The man's death is being treated as suspicious and a woman, 27, is in police custody.
The man has not yet been formally identified and an investigation is on going.
